caption.paragraph:
FIGURE 37.

Oniphenes lobanovi


gen. et sp. nov
.

, orig. A–D: paratype, female from QLD (“… Cape Tribulation area, 21–28 Mar. 1984 
…
”), E–H: holotype, male from QLD (“Cairns”) and I: paratype, female from QLD (“… Cape Tribulation area, 1–11 May 1992 …”); 
A
: body, dorsal; 
B
: head, dorsal; 
C
: head and thorax, ventral; 
D
: lateral side of abdominal segments 5 and 6, dorsal; 
E
: male anal sclerite and 
spiculum gastrale
, ventral; 
F
: tegmen, ventral; 
G
: penis trunk, dorsal; 
H
: proximal part of inner sac with armature; 
I
: ovipositor, ventral. Scale bars: 
a
= 0.5 mm to Fig. A; 
b
= 0.5 mm to Figs B–D; 
с
= 0.25 mm to Figs E–I.
